narratives.question_text: What knowledge, skills, and insights did you develop by taking this course?
comments: I further improved my piano skills with the wonderful Prof. Wei-Yi Yang. Humanizing my approach to the music really helped this semester. I was also introduced to various opera styles as context for improving certain pieces, which was really insightful.

narratives.question_text: What are the strengths and weaknesses of this course and how could it be improved?
comments: All good! I thoroughly enjoyed the lessons even through stressful testing periods.

narratives.question_text: Would you recommend this course to another student? Please explain.
comments: If you're considering a classical music path, definitely!
